theorem Topology.isOpen_of_subset_interior
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    (A : Set X) ⊆ interior A → IsOpen A := by
  intro h
  have hEq : interior A = A := Set.Subset.antisymm interior_subset h
  simpa [hEq] using isOpen_interior

theorem Topology.interior_interior_closure_eq_interior_closure
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    interior (interior (closure A)) = interior (closure A) := by
  simpa [interior_interior]
